# 数轴覆盖

![][image_ref_814hhbdi]

## 思路1:暴力遍历 ,O(n<sup>2</sup>)
```java
public static int solutionA(int[]nums,int L) {
		int count = 0;
		for(int i=0;i<nums.length;i++) {
			int temp = L;
			int count2 =0;
			for(int j=i;j<nums.length;j++) {
				if(nums[j]-nums[i]<=temp) {
					count2=count2>j-i+1?count2:j-i+1;
				}else {
					break;
				}
				
			}
			
			count=count>count2?count:count2;
		}
			
		
		return count;
	}
```
## 思路2:双指针 ,O(n),每个指针指遍历过一次即可
```java
public static int solutionB(int[]nums,int L) {
   int count =0;
   int left=0;
   int right=0;
   while(left<nums.length) {
      for(;right<nums.length;right++) {
         if(nums[right]-nums[left]<=L) {}
         else break;
      }
      right--; //不符合规则，回退一位
      count=Math.max(count, right-left+1);
      left++;
      
   }
   
   return count;
}
```
